data.description: Fantastic opportunity to own an immaculate, move in ready home, in the ever-popular gate community of Veranda Gardens! This 4BR/2BA/2CG home was built in 2021 and sits on a lovely lot with views overlooking the canal. Open great room floorplan is light & bright including kitchen w/ white cabinetry, quartz counters, SS appliances, wall oven, center island, spacious pantry, pendant lighting, gas cooktop, elegant vent hood & tile backsplash. Master bedroom overlooks the back yard, has a large walk-in closet and ensuite w/ dual sinks & spa-like walk in tiled shower w/ frameless glass. Other special features include wood look tile flooring throughout, custom lighting, plantation shutters, neutral interior paint, IMPACT GLASS throughout, fenced yard, glass insert front door and more. The screened and covered patio leads to the spacious back yard that is already fenced for your furry family members. Plenty of room to add a pool or you can just head to the beautiful community pool to meet up with friends and neighbors! Veranda gardens is a gated community nestled minutes from Palm City & Stuart with plentiful amenities including a clubhouse with fitness center, multiple pools, dog park, playground, pickleball, tennis, fire pit, outdoor bar/dining area, grilling areas and more. Great location to interstates, beaches, shopping, restaurants and schools. Call today to view!
